==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stound
<hw>Stound</hw> <pr>(stound)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Astound</er>, <er>Stun</er>.]</ety> <def>To be in pain or
sorrow.</def> <mark>[Obs. or Prov. Eng. & Scot.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

